# üö® Build Prevention Rules (MANDATORY)

## ‚ùå NEVER commit code with:

* Unused variables, imports, or parameters (use `_` prefix or remove)
* Missing `alt` attributes on images
* Using `<img>` instead of Next.js `<Image>`
* Unescaped quotes in JSX
* Using `any` type
* Missing dependencies in `useEffect`/`useCallback`
* Async params in Next.js 15 not awaited

## ‚úÖ ALWAYS:

* Use `<Image>` with `alt`
* Remove unused code before committing
* Use specific, strict types
* Await all async destructured values
* Run `pnpm run build` locally before commit
* Fix all TypeScript errors
* Escape JSX quotes properly
* Format with Prettier and lint with ESLint

## PowerShell Compatibility (MANDATORY)

* Use `;` instead of `&&`
* Validate CLI commands in Windows PowerShell
* Avoid Bash-specific syntax in pnpm scripts
